{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, I went back, when I worked in the fields, I went back to sleep in Wojciu's.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I brought potatoes, and I-- and I brought bread, or whatever milk they gave me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they were kind people, they told me, OK, I asked them, I said, can I come and work in your house?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said-- Because they thought when I was working with them that I was a Ukrainian or Polish girl, but they knew eventually that I was a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I will give you an example.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a stove in Poland, in this little shack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was made out of stones, and there was a plate, an iron plate, and an opening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You put the wood, or whatever you had in there, and the plate heated up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you took a potato, and you [? slice ?] very thin pieces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You put them and baked them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you were so hungry that when your turn came to pick up that little piece of potato, you burned your fingers-- you burnt your tongue because you were so hungry, you couldn't wait for it to cool off.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when I lay down, I put my fist in my stomach so that my intestines, when they fell over and they hurt me, they should be stopped.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was very, very hungry, and when I was given a piece of bread, I never even took a crumb.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I brought it to my mother, my mother divided it up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Wojciu used to get some things, so we cooked a soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were liberated--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But again, that was in March of 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
